{
  "stem": "21582.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we always felt that they are luring us, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who knows? s we knew that there was-- we thought that-- I don't know if there were any guards or not.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we thought that there were guards there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we-- we-- we met-- in Skarzysko, we met two of my cousins who were from-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I can't think-- from a different town.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- we did not really know them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we-- we knew them through letters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we never saw them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother knew-- knew them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my parents communicated-- but these two brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, they were all right in terms, they were able to smuggle in with them some-- some of their jewelry, some gold.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- they-- they-- they-- did not-- they did not starve.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But anyway, we joined them in their barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we just sat there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We went into their barracks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we kept on hearing more and more detonation from-- from the distance.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "At some point, one or several of the men would step-- step outside the barrack and came back, hey, you know, there's no reaction from the outside.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So they dared to go a little bit further.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then they came back and reported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And slowly, they reached the gate at night and there was-- and there was-- the gates where unguarded.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But nobody-- we did not-- maybe some people dared out a little distance, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was a very gradual slow kind of testing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the meantime, at night, the-- we-- the bombardment came closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, all I remember of that bombardment, the-- the-- it was very unthreatening to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because it was like Messiah was coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
